ESXi Installation
=================

- Download ESXi
- Set up HW-RAID
- Install ESXi
- Setup
  + ConfigureNetwork Management
    * Network Adapters: vmnic2 (tertiary card)
    * IPv4: 10.41.7.4X/24
    * IPv6: Disabled
    * DNS: 10.41.7.1
    * Hostname: virt1
- Log in to Web UI
- Disks: ssd, hdd
- Network: vSwitch1-Guest:
  + Both links
  + 2_Standard
  + 3_Guest
  + 50_Production
  + 51_DMZ
  + 7_Infrastructure
- Upload Debian ISO
- Assign License
